"{\"uid\": \"today.com-news-paris-olympics-stephen-nedoroscik-elmo-rcna165445\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"A Michael Kors Bag, Suede Slippers and More Holiday Gifts at Walmart - Starting at $9    Gina Vivinetto  A sweet online exchange between Elmo andU.S.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 149, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2, \"end\": 14, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Kors\", \"score\": 0.9999972290417838, \"rank\": 2.770965736591923e-06, \"text\": \"Michael Kors\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Kors\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Kors\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"gymnast Stephen Nedoroscikis melting fans' hearts during the 2024 Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 150, \"to\": 231, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The red furry \\\"Sesame Street\\\" character, who's been hobnobbing with Olympians since he arrived in Paris, reached out on X to Nedoroscik to ask him for advice about how to specialize in an activity.\", \"from\": 233, \"to\": 430, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 331, \"end\": 336, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999948458935, \"rank\": 5.153970917345936e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Mr. Stephen Nedoroscik, Elmo wants to be a specialist too!\", \"from\": 432, \"to\": 491, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 437, \"end\": 455, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephen_Nedoroscik\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stephen Nedoroscik\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephen_Nedoroscik\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephen_Nedoroscik\"}, {\"begin\": 457, \"end\": 461, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elmo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.864468759057991e-30, \"text\": \"Elmo\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elmo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elmo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Elmo was thinking he could be the giggle specialist or maybe a monster-hug specialist.\", \"from\": 492, \"to\": 578, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Elmo will keep thinking!\", \"from\": 579, \"to\": 603, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 579, \"end\": 583, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elmo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.864468759057991e-30, \"text\": \"Elmo\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elmo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elmo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"wrotethe Muppet.\", \"from\": 603, \"to\": 620, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Thebronze medal winnerreplied with encouragement for Elmo, telling him he could do anything he set his heart out to do.\", \"from\": 622, \"to\": 741, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 675, \"end\": 679, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elmo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.864468759057991e-30, \"text\": \"Elmo\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elmo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elmo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Elmo, the great thing about specializing in something is you get to decide,\\\" hewrote.\", \"from\": 743, \"to\": 829, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think you will be a great specialist in anything you end up choosing!\\\"\", \"from\": 830, \"to\": 903, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Elmo in turn wrote back, \\\"Thank you, Mr. Steve!\", \"from\": 905, \"to\": 952, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You are so kind!\", \"from\": 953, \"to\": 969, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Elmo is now the official specialist of giggles!!!!!!!\", \"from\": 970, \"to\": 1023, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ha ha ha!\", \"from\": 1024, \"to\": 1033, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Elmo loves you!\\\"\", \"from\": 1034, \"to\": 1050, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"X users responded by saying the pair's adorable exchange tugged at their heartstrings.\", \"from\": 1052, \"to\": 1138, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Oh okay.\", \"from\": 1140, \"to\": 1149, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So we are just crying on a random Tuesday because Stephen gave Elmo the special boost to be WHATEVER HE WANTED,\\\" read one response.\", \"from\": 1150, \"to\": 1281, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You are fantastically wholesome,\\\" another user told Nedoroscik, \\\"and please know that's intended as a massive compliment.\\\"\", \"from\": 1283, \"to\": 1406, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Some called the pair's conversation \\\"pure,\\\" with one writing, \\\"i need this whole thing printed on a tshirt.\\\"\", \"from\": 1408, \"to\": 1516, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Others said they hoped to see Nedoroscik, whom fans nicknamed \\\"Pommel Horse Guy\\\" after witnessing his gymnastics skills in Paris, on an upcoming  \\\"Sesame Street\\\" episode.\", \"from\": 1518, \"to\": 1688, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1641, \"end\": 1646, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999948458935, \"rank\": 5.153970917345936e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think someone needs to make an appearance on Sesame Street pronto!\", \"from\": 1690, \"to\": 1759, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Make it happen, @elmo !\", \"from\": 1760, \"to\": 1783, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"@sesamestreet,\\\" one wrote.\", \"from\": 1784, \"to\": 1810, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While at the Olympics, Elmo and his \\\"Sesame Street\\\" pals have been meeting up with members of Team USA, includinggold medal-winning gymnasts Simone Biles, Suni Lee and Jordan Chiles.\", \"from\": 1812, \"to\": 1994, \"entities\":